sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as install.go
    participant Wizard as runInstallWizard
    participant Core as core.Config
    participant Docker as docker.Client
    participant FS as filesystem

    User->>CLI: newapi install --interactive
    CLI->>Core: GetConfig()
    CLI->>Wizard: runInstallWizard(cfg)

    Note over Wizard: Step 1/7: 端口
    Wizard->>User: [1/7] 请选择端口 (默认 3000)
    User->>Wizard: 8080

    Note over Wizard: Step 2/7: 域名
    Wizard->>User: [2/7] 域名 (可选, 默认无)
    User->>Wizard: api.example.com

    Note over Wizard: Step 3/7: 数据库
    Wizard->>User: [3/7] 数据库类型 (mysql/sqlite)
    User->>Wizard: mysql

    Note over Wizard: Step 4/7: Redis
    Wizard->>User: [4/7] Redis 地址 (默认 redis:6379)
    User->>Wizard: (Enter)

    Note over Wizard: Step 5/7: 镜像
    Wizard->>User: [5/7] Docker 镜像 (默认 calciumion/new-api:latest)
    User->>Wizard: (Enter)

    Note over Wizard: Step 6/7: 镜像加速
    Wizard->>User: [6/7] 是否自动选择最快镜像? (Y/n)
    User->>Wizard: Y

    Note over Wizard: Step 7/7: 确认
    Wizard->>User: 显示配置摘要 + "确认安装? (Y/n)"
    User->>Wizard: Y

    Wizard-->>CLI: opts (installOptions)

    CLI->>Docker: ImagePull(image)
    Docker-->>CLI: pull complete

    CLI->>FS: WriteFile(docker-compose.yml)
    CLI->>FS: WriteFile(.env)

    CLI->>Docker: ComposeUp(home)
    Docker-->>CLI: containers started

    CLI->>CLI: waitForHealth(port)
    CLI-->>User: 安装完成摘要
